| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-4980 — Recovery Inhibition (stormous)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 36cee208-f2a6-5e2c-a9eb-266bf4d6805f"
